Disk /dev/md1: 21.4 GB, 21476081664 bytes
			</screen>
			<para>You can also use <command>fdisk</command> to obtain information about one specific hard disk device.</para>
			<screen>
[root@rhel4 ~]# fdisk -l /dev/sda

