		<section><title>/sbin/lsscsi</title>
			<para>The <command>/sbin/lsscsi</command><indexterm><primary>lsscsi(1)</primary></indexterm> will gve you a nice readable output of all scsi (and scsi emulated devices). This first screenshot shows lsscsi on a SPARC system.</para>
